start2016.com/image/2020/02/06/1580978862387532.jpg\" style=\"width: 754px; height: 958px;\" title=\"1580978862387050146.jpg\" width=\"754\" height=\"958\"/></p><p><img src=\"http://www.start2016.com/image/2020/02/06/1580978862507027.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"1580978862507089358.jpg\"/></p><p><img src=\"http://www.start2016.com/image/2020/02/06/1580978862504094.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"1580978862504071931.jpg\"/></p><p><img src=\"http://www.start2016.com/image/2020/02/06/1580978862565373.jpg\" style=\"width: 809px; height: 958px;\" title=\"1580978862565067092.jpg\" width=\"809\" height=\"958\"/></p><p><img src=\"http://www.start2016.com/image/2020/02/06/1580978862765616.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"1580978862765032078.jpg\"/></p><p><img src=\"http://www.start2016.com/image/2020/02/06/1580978862777695.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"1580978862777084472.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p>','2020-02-06 16:48:05'),(115,'xyfczs','石龙杰同学谈学习体会','http://www.start2016.com/image/2020/02/06/1580977586675276.jpg','','<p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong><img src=\"http://www.start2016.com/image/2020/02/06/1580977574865995.jpg\" title=\"1580977574865072129.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_20170612_163859.jpg\"/></strong></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong>石龙杰同学的感言：感谢合肥起航电气设计培训班的培养，通过为期3个月的学习，我真正掌握了一门技术，再也不用担心找工作了。目前我又考取了浙江科技学院的研究生，继续深造，希望以后再电气设计行业做出一定的成绩。加油，学弟学妹们。</strong></span><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong><br/></strong></span></p><p><br/></p>','2020-02-06 16:56:18'),(117,'gywm','关于我们',NULL,'','<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp; <span style=\"font-size: 26px; box-sizing: border-box;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;合肥锐衡教育咨询有限公司简介</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; color: rgb(90, 90, 90); white-space: normal; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑, Helvetica, 黑体, Arial, Tahoma; font-size: 12px; text-align: center; line-height: 28px; background: white;\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 13px; padding: 0px; border: none; color: rgb(90, 90, 90); white-space: normal; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑, Helvetica, 黑体, Arial, Tahoma; font-size: 12px; text-indent: 37px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 楷体; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 20px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">&nbsp;合肥锐衡教育咨询有限公司【原合肥起航电气设计工作室】，自2013开始逐步发展，2016年网站正式上线运行，</span><span style=\"font-family: 楷体; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 20px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">2019年8月正式注册为：合肥锐衡教育咨询有限公司，公司经营范围：文化教育咨询、服务，人力资源开发，企业人才推荐、人才委培及能力提升，实习岗位推荐、实习生技能提升拓展，CAD图纸设计制作、电气项目图纸设计制作、自动化项目图纸设计及编程、广告设计制作发布代理，教育产品研发及销售、教育软件开发及销售；计算机硬件、软件技术开发、技术服务；电子产品研发、销售；知识产权服务；教育项目与教育科研文献研发；&nbsp;目前已经开展的业务：</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 13px; padding: 0px; border: none; color: rgb(90, 90, 90); white-space: normal; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑, Helvetica, 黑体, Arial, Tahoma; font-size: 12px; text-indent: 37px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 楷体; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 20px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">1.建筑电气设计培训及咨询服务；</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 13px; padding: 0px; border: none; color: rgb(90, 90, 90); white-space: normal; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑, Helvetica, 黑体, Arial, Tahoma; font-size: 12px; text-indent: 37px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 楷体; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 20px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">2.室外夜景亮化照明施工图培训；</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 13px; padding: 0px; border: none; color: rgb(90, 90, 90); white-space: normal; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑, Helvetica, 黑体, Arial, Tahoma; font-size: 12px; text-indent: 37px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 楷体; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 20px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">3.<span style=\"font-family: 楷体; font-size: 20px; text-indent: 37px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">电气工程公司等新员工入职电气技能培训；</span></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 13px; padding: 0px; border: none; color: rgb(90, 90, 90); white-space: normal; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑, Helvetica, 黑体, Arial, Tahoma; font-size: 12px; text-indent: 37px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 楷体; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 20px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">4.承接建筑电气施工图设计；&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 13px; padding: 0px; border: none; color: rgb(90, 90, 90); white-space: normal; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑, Helvetica, 黑体, Arial, Tahoma; font-size: 12px; text-indent: 37px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 楷体; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 20px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">5.承接室外夜景亮化电气施工图设计；</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 13px; padding: 0px; border: none; color: rgb(90, 90, 90); white-space: normal; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑, Helvetica, 黑体, Arial, Tahoma; font-size: 12px; text-indent: 37px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 楷体; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 20px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">6.注册电气工程师考试（基础考试）培训；&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 13px; padding: 0px; border: none; color: rgb(90, 90, 90); white-space: normal; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑, Helvetica, 黑体, Arial, Tahoma; font-size: 12px; text-indent: 37px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 楷体; font-size: 20px;\">7.国家电网考试培训；&nbsp;</span><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 13px; padding: 0px; border: none; color: rgb(90, 90, 90); white-space: normal; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑, Helvetica, 黑体, Arial, Tahoma; font-size: 12px; text-indent: 37px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 楷体; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 20px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">公司聘请：安建大副教授（国家注册电气工程师）、安建大讲师、安徽省建科院设计院高工（高级工程师）等实战派设计高手任专职讲师。以理论教学为基础，以实际工程项目做案例，手把手教会学员把握设计思路、掌握电气施工图设计技巧，通过培训使学员能够切实掌握一门技术，毕业后快速融入到公司的技术团队中，成为公司的独挡一面的技术骨干。俗话说：“不怕百门通，就怕一门精”、“荒年饿不死手艺人”，作为一名未来的工程师，只有掌握一门实用技术，才能在社会上立足，才能成为是社会需要的人才，没人任何特长之人，只能被社会淘汰。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 13px; padding: 0px; border: none; color: rgb(90, 90, 90); white-space: normal; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑, Helvetica, 黑体, Arial, Tahoma; font-size: 12px; text-indent: 37px; line-height: 3em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 楷体; font-size: 20px; text-indent: 0px;\">公司拥有一支具有多年电气设计经验的团队，可以承担：建筑电气施工图纸设计、家装二次施工图设计、室外夜景亮化照明施工图设计，欢迎新老客户联系洽谈；</span><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 13px; padding: 0px; border: none; color: rgb(90, 90, 90); white-space: normal; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑, Helvetica, 黑体, Arial, Tahoma; font-size: 12px; text-indent: 37px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 楷体; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 20px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">合肥市经济技术开发区蓬莱花园23栋（安徽建筑大学南区北门西100米）<br/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; color: rgb(90, 90, 90); white-space: normal; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑, Helvetica, 黑体, Arial, Tahoma; font-size: 12px; background: white; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 楷体; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 20px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">网址：</span><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; cursor: pointer; background: 0px 0px; font-family: 楷体; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 20px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><a href=\"http://www.start2016.com/\" style=\"text-decoration: underline; cursor: pointer; background: 0px 0px; font-family: 楷体; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 20px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">www.start2016.com</a></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; color: rgb(90, 90, 90); white-space: normal; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑, Helvetica, 黑体, Arial, Tahoma; font-size: 12px; background: white; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 楷体; font-size: 20px;\">咨询QQ:16653162</span><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; color: rgb(90, 90, 90); white-space: normal; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑, Helvetica, 黑体, Arial, Tahoma; font-size: 12px; background: white; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 楷体; font-size: 20px;\">锐衡电气设计报名群号: 727013424</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; color: rgb(90, 90, 90); white-space: normal; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑, Helvetica, 黑体, Arial, Tahoma; font-size: 12px; background: white; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 楷体; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 